  "description": "A stunning aerial view captures a vibrant sunset over a coastal city and bay. The sun, a brilliant orange orb, is partially obscured by distant hills, creating a dramatic golden glow that reflects on the water. Wispy, layered clouds streak across the sky in shades of orange, pink, and deep blue. Below, a sprawling cityscape of closely packed buildings extends to the shoreline. The foreground is dominated by silhouetted trees and foliage, adding depth and framing the expansive view. Long, radiant sunbeams extend from the sun across the sky, enhancing the majestic quality of the scene.",
